    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Type series of (A) Cnemaspis rishivalleyensis sp. nov. (from left to right, NCBS-BH724, NCBS-BH725, NCBS- BH627, NCBS-BH626,) and (B) type series of Hemidactylus rishivalleyensis sp. nov. (from left to right, NCBS-BH729, NCBS- BH730, NCBS-BH631, NCBS-BH632, NCBS-BH633, NCBS-BH634, NCBS-BH635,). Scale bars 10 mm." ;
