<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4486620>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Cnemaspis rishivalleyensis sp. nov. (holotype, NCBS-BH723), (A) dorsal view of body, (B) ventral view of body, (C) dorsal view of tail, and (D) ventral view of tail. Scale bars 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4486620/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4486622>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Cnemaspis rishivalleyensis sp. nov. (holotype, NCBS-BH723), (A) dorsal view of head, (B) ventral view of head, (C) lateral view of head, (D) view of cloacal region showing precloacal and femoral pores, (E) ventral view of right manus, and (F) ventral view of right pes. Scale bars 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4486622/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4486624>
